Very short viva explanation
If teacher says “Explain your program,” you can say:
“This program creates a web page containing an image, a hyperlink, and a nested table. The image is displayed using the img tag, the hyperlink is created using the a tag, and a table is placed inside another table to demonstrate a nested table.”
