Common viva questions
1. What is HTML?
HTML stands for HyperText Markup Language.
2. Which tag is used to display an image?
<img>
3. What is the use of src in image tag?
It specifies the path of the image.
4. What is the use of alt?
It displays alternate text if the image does not load.
5. Which tag is used to create a hyperlink?
<a>
6. What is href?
It specifies the link destination.
7. What is a nested table?
A table inside another table.
8. What is the difference between th and td?
•	th = heading cell 
•	td = normal data cell 
